{
  "name": "Armorsmith Kit",
  "type": "tool",
  "img": "icons/containers/bags/pouch-leather-gold-grey.webp",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><span dir=\"ltr\">This Kit contains all the necessary implements to create armor of varying types.</span></p><p><span dir=\"ltr\">Proficiency with this kit allows you to add your proficiency bonus to all checks involving this kit and also allows you to do the following; Craft Armor and Armor Seals.</span></p><p><span dir=\"ltr\">While you have access to this kit, each time you would attempt to Craft armor or an Armor Seal, you spend a charge of your Armorsmith kit as some tools break, become brittle or have wear and tear on them.</span></p><p><span dir=\"ltr\">This kit grants a creature the ability to create up to C- Rank Armor Seals.</span></p><p><span dir=\"ltr\">Higher quality Armorsmith Kits, will allow a creature to create higher ranked armor seals at reduced ryo OR downtime costs as seen on the Armorsmith Chart on the following page.</span></p><p><span dir=\"ltr\">If this would reduce the total downtime cost of an item to 0, you would instead only spend 1 week.</span></p><p></p><p>Swift Craft DC: 24</p>",
      "chat": ""
    },
